title: Ep 41 :: Live From China!
itunes:title: Live From China!
description: Frank broadcasts from Shanghai as he visits some of the biggest cities in China. Is the growth for real? Will Chinese commercial real estate collapse? Plus, Stephanie Link, Director of Research at TheStreet.com, talks about recent earnings and several catalysts that could push stocks higher.

itunes:subtitle: Frank reports from China as the Phase 1 Investor team take a research trip through Hong Kong, Macau, and Shanghai. Guest Stephanie Link, Director of Research at theStreet.com, talks with Frank about the recent Wall Street selloff.
